data.description: FULLY ASSUMABLE MORTGAGE capable at a 3.75% interest rate! Incredible, newer home in the highly sought after neighborhood of West Tampa! Open floor plan, 3 bedroom/2 bath, concrete block construction built in 2015. This home features tile flooring through the whole house with luxury vinyl plank in the bedrooms, vaulted ceilings which create an atmosphere of openness, energy efficient impact windows & sliders and an indoor laundry room with cabinets and granite countertop for extra storage and daily chore convenience. The kitchen, which is the heart of the home, features beautiful granite countertops and an island/bar that opens to the great room for the perfect, open entertainment space. The kitchen also features stainless-steel appliances including refrigerator, range, microwave, and dishwasher. The large master bedroom has a spacious walk-in closet and a serene private bathroom featuring double vanities, granite countertop, spa-like tub and generously sized shower. When you step outside, the property continues to delight with a paver driveway, 2-car garage, a covered back patio and fenced yard for privacy and outdoor activities.   This incredible home is in the heart of West Tampa, walking distance to Raymond James Stadium, close to Mid-town, Armature Works, Hyde Park, International Mall, restaurants, shops, nearby major hospitals, and Interstate 275. What's more, the convenience of being just minutes away from Tampa International Airport ensuring an easy commute! In addition, NO HOA or CDD Fees. Call today and schedule your private showing appointment! Don’t hesitate as this remarkable home will not last long! Make this house your HOME!
